{"tid":2455884,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新義安蝻亞於觀塘狗屋確診武肺","createTime":"2021-03-21T12:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T17:23:37.000Z","uid":303304,"like":424,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"5b847829f3e35855df3f1254f2f69f8c14392064","tid":2455884,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"沒源頭確診武漢肺炎的26歲新義安巴裔男子，日前與逾百名同黨到鯉魚門「曬馬」時被捕，體內有抗體、病毒量低，或早已染疫。因他拒絕合作，政府未能確定他與同黨接觸有多緊密，曾扣留警署的16名同黨須隔離檢疫。消息指，社團內人心惶惶「驚到震」，擔心患者曾接觸並播毒其他成員，至少30名新義安秀茂坪成員自行檢測。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鯉魚門三家村牌坊一帶日前有大批黑漢為爭奪地盤利益，吹雞「曬馬」集結，醞釀廝殺。警方派大批軍裝到場，拘捕17人，包括該名染疫男。雖然該男子報稱不適，直接送院，但其16名同黨則押返觀塘警署。當聯合醫院通知警方，該男子初步確診後，警方立即批准16人保釋，並消毒警署。至於可能與確診男緊密接觸的15名警員則須檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0d9f062c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM%2F&h=b2a9a9d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM/</a>"},{"pid":"9cdc751a5dc43e731bfcca48d1dd1e5a358f5cad","tid":2455884,"uid":303304,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"曾夥逾百同黨曬馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170f2a024642c8e62b16b396e2205f29295a7eee","tid":2455884,"uid":303304,"like":238,"dislike":4,"score":234,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"鄉黑crossover 狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個群組叫咩名好<img src=\"/a