結，醞釀廝殺。警方派大批軍裝到場，拘捕17人，包括該名染疫男。雖然該男子報稱不適，直接送院，但其16名同黨則押返觀塘警署。當聯合醫院通知警方，<span class=\"red\">該男子初步確診後，警方立即批准16人保釋，並消毒警署</span>。至於可能與確診男緊密接觸的15名警員則須檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0d9f062c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210321%2F73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM%2F&h=b2a9a9d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210321/73S4ESOSJBAWRGELTNHJH53CWM/</a></blockquote><br />\n咁撚兒戲既？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放出黎野公眾？"},{"pid":"9922be4398ab94347fd4df6282b3c6e68aa6866b","tid":2455884,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"170f2a024642c8e62b16b396e2205f29295a7eee","tid":2455884,"uid":303304,"like":238,"dislike":4,"score":234,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"鄉黑crossover 狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個群組叫咩名好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"雙黑群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77cbbf12234255d1281f39b379cf04d34b9e4bd","tid":2455884,"uid":388282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"真手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=